{"tid":838420,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我的濕疹日記，圖文記錄（慎入","createTime":"2018-09-27T06:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T17:03:40.000Z","uid":113678,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc03c35acbdaf6c34f30a0a35a1fba6c3cbd959","tid":838420,"uid":113678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:01:52.000Z","msg":"幾年前讀中學開始有濕疹<br />\n到呢年先好番 冇再爛肉 唔洗再r☺<br />\n全身幾乎咩位置都發過<br />\n以前病得太西利冇心情打<br />\n雖然宜家都係冇咩心情😰<br />\n但希望所有仲受緊折磨既人唔好放棄<br />\n回想當初都係有人鼓勵 支持我<br />\n我先的起心肝試新野 研究病因 冇放棄❤<br />\n<br />\n得閒會up相 目標呢個星期做到一半<br />\n盡量跟時序講起啦<br />\n太舊既相可能冇 因為換過手機冇save低<br />\n<br />\n有人話濕疹&ldquo;係唔會好得番架 跟你一世架&ldquo;<br />\n但起碼我知自己好得番<br />\n將來會唔會番發我唔肯定<br />\n我相信心存希望，正能量<br />\n找到對的人 對的藥 對的方法 <br />\n一定可以擺脫病魔，心魔<br />\n<br />\n大家加油 共勉之☺ <br />\ntg @noonelovesme"},{"pid":"707e12d95057d263066c2b68fccd4640a4ba0e01","tid":838420,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"圖呢?我都有少少唔知係咪濕疹<br />\n沖完涼會紅同痕<br />\n平時唔搞佢無野<br />\n不過會生到皮膚一忽忽"},{"pid":"7fe7be1684143b0df28d3f56e510dab94e5850df","tid":838420,"uid":60206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"唔知我果D 算唔算濕疹, 得乜D 位有<br />\n大脾LA 位成日(其實都差唔多係日日)都好痕, 有時都會R 到損<br />\n<br />\n唔知巴打用咩醫返好?"},{"pid":"11144e40bc54c9b4d025a3d7f6f97a809492161d","tid":838420,"uid":208854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"707e12d95057d263066c2b68fccd4640a4ba0e01","tid":838420,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"圖呢?我都有少少唔知係咪濕疹<br />\n沖完涼會紅同痕<br />\n平時唔搞佢無野<br />\n不過會生到皮膚一忽忽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"係咪 紅色 有啲似個圈咁？"},{"pid":"5097a94e11f57baffdf5cc080979db5d252a184d","tid":838420,"uid":190862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"腳底有一堆小水泡<br />\n好密望到都覺得恐怖呢D係咪都係濕疹黎"},{"pid":"ef0f815c992c5450ebc7ecddbbde62f36c75b129","tid":838420,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"留名，我都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dac3f477b21e598036ac83a66dcc2e8f74c66b","tid":838420,"uid":208516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"我係初中個陣都有濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但淨係得塊面同條頸有<br />\n啲濕疹真係好痕，痕到我r損曬，流咗啲黃色嘅水岀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經過2年幾之後就好番曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5104fdda2f3bd10ca8b71c46cd748e7eda9d24a3","tid":838420,"uid":113678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"707e12d95057d263066c2b68fccd4640a4ba0e01","tid":838420,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"圖呢?我都有少少唔知係咪濕疹<br />\n沖完涼會紅同痕<br />\n平時唔搞佢無野<br />\n不過會生到皮膚一忽忽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/noonelovesme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnoonelovesme&d=qy6Ry%2FISLpotfIeQJdc3d26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f6a07064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/noonelovesme</a><br />\nsubscribe住先 今晚放工開始搞<br />\n第一次開channel 等我摸索一下"},{"pid":"03f600bc164e47f5a0df6ff3de3013cf8b4381a5","tid":838420,"uid":123103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:21:26.000Z","msg":"講下點樣醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e023069b6f2a468b067879df186edcfe3b2485","tid":838420,"uid":113678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f600bc164e47f5a0df6ff3de3013cf8b4381a5","tid":838420,"uid":123103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:21:26.000Z","msg":"講下點樣醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"會呀<br />\noh sorry你想我倒序講起？"},{"pid":"bdc8b9483dedf16da69a95766efb8534dbab6ccd","tid":838420,"uid":123